@startuml
title Horizon Bank customer-acquisition value stream cross-map

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ranksep 15
skinparam ArrowColor #334155
skinparam ArrowFontColor #1E293B
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
  RoundCorner 8
}

rectangle "STAKEHOLDER\nRetail Customer\nNeed: establish a banking relationship" as CUSTOMER #E0F2FE

rectangle "STAGE 1  Need understood\nValue added: suitable direction is clear\nPrimary: Relationship Management\nSupporting: Digital Servicing\nBIAN 14.0: assess candidate Service Domains and interactions" as S1 #F8FAFC
rectangle "STAGE 2  Application established\nValue added: intent and evidence can proceed\nPrimary: Document Capture\nSupporting: Digital Servicing\nBIAN 14.0: assess candidate Service Domains and interactions" as S2 #F8FAFC
rectangle "STAGE 3  Identity and eligibility confirmed\nValue added: governed decision is supported\nPrimary: Identity Verification | Risk Assessment\nSupporting: Financial Crime Screening\nBIAN 14.0: assess candidate Service Domains and interactions" as S3 #FEF3C7
rectangle "STAGE 4  Banking relationship established\nValue added: authoritative relationship records exist\nPrimary: Party Management | Account Opening\nSupporting: none in this selected view\nBIAN 14.0: assess candidate Service Domains and interactions" as S4 #F8FAFC
rectangle "STAGE 5  Services ready to use\nValue added: agreed service can be used\nPrimary: Digital Servicing\nSupporting: Notification Management | Account Servicing\nBIAN 14.0: assess candidate Service Domains and interactions" as S5 #F8FAFC

rectangle "OUTCOME\nUsable banking relationship" as OUTCOME #DCFCE7

CUSTOMER -down-> S1 : seeks value through
S1 -down-> S2 : contributes to
S2 -down-> S3 : contributes to
S3 -down-> S4 : contributes to
S4 -down-> S5 : contributes to
S5 -down-> OUTCOME : contributes to

note bottom
  Capability contributions enable stages; they do not equal stages.
  BIAN mappings are candidate, partial and many-to-many.
  A Service Domain is not a value stage, process step, application or microservice.
end note
@enduml
